{"tid":1633773,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"教育局：要求全港中學交戴口罩學生人數","createTime":"2019-10-07T05:12:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T01:37:39.000Z","uid":20933,"like":6,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"d314d4536e816147846a7a25868f1086c7cd0c3c","tid":1633773,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:12:43.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】教育局要求全港中學周二提交罷課或戴口罩學生人數，中學校長會主席鄧振強相信教育局是希望掌握學生的情緒。<br />\n<br />\n鄧振強：「他們只是需要提供一個大約的數字，大約的數字可能是以十位數為單位，不需要精準到71個、72個、73個，不會再跟學校核實這些數字。第二我們是不需要提交學生的名字，這個要特別去澄清，不然學生可能會很緊張會有秋後算帳這樣的情況。我不想有太多的陰謀論籠罩着這個社會，我們要用平常心去看，我們只是提交一個大約的數字，讓教育局去掌握全港學校大致學生情緒的趨勢。」"},{"pid":"7640c1302ac6cf2e9d87ffbeb638bb03029d9fd3","tid":1633773,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:12:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/editorsChoice/player?newsId=365360\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D365360&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4sRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=a0b3adad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D365360&h=b3c047a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/editorsChoice/player?newsId=365360</a>"},{"pid":"61284bd4dcf4fd6f4884f5a5bef5a161f12450ff","tid":1633773,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:13:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0392b49712fbe3a5ba5bbc03c18c139bbee4e145","tid":1633773,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:13:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2403f72d7ba83b46a799e9411aa3e147de0b6afe","tid":1633773,"uid":25468,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:13:50.000Z","msg":"法律上學校都唔係公共場所 , 學校戴口罩唔犯法"},{"pid":"dd0647d1200321828b309e42140db252037bd0d4","tid":1633773,"uid":19527,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:13:56.000Z","msg":"咁就要多啲人帶喇<i